@@ -0,0 +1,46 @@
+/*
+ * Device Tree Source for the Draak board
+ *
+ * Copyright (C) 2016 Renesas Electronics Corp.
+ * Copyright (C) 2017 Glider bvba
+ *
+ * This file is licensed under the terms of the GNU General Public License
